phdl.parser
Class PinDeclaration

java.lang.Object
  phdl.parser.Element
      phdl.parser.Declarable
          phdl.parser.ArrayDeclaration
              phdl.parser.PinDeclaration

public class PinDeclaration
extends ArrayDeclaration

A class that represents a pin declaration in phdl. In addition to inherited fields, a pin declaration has a type, and a string containing a pin list.

Author:
Richard Black and Brad Riching
